    "description":  "Information for candidates applying for the Commercial Lawyer vacancy in GCHQ ",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"headline-information\"\u003eHeadline Information\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDepartment\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGovernment Communications Headquarters (\u003cabbr title=\"Government Communications Headquarters\"\u003eGCHQ\u003c/abbr\u003e)\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDivision\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLegal Team\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eJob title\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCommercial Lawyer\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLocation\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCheltenham or London\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eSalary\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGrade 7 - £54,532 plus £5,500 London Pay Addition if applicable\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eApplication deadline\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eMonday 4 March 2019\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"vacancy-details\"\u003eVacancy details\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs one of Britain’s intelligence agencies, \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.gchq.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Government Communications Headquarters\"\u003eGCHQ\u003c/abbr\u003e\u003c/a\u003e unlock the complex world of communications to keep our nation safe.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe work closely with \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.mi5.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMI5\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.sis.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMI6\u003c/a\u003e, our partners in the intelligence community, to safeguard Britain’s people, interests and businesses from various threats. Think cyber-attacks, espionage, terrorism, and organised crime.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt’s challenging, varied and meaningful work that you simply won’t find anywhere else.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe are currently recruiting for a number of lawyers to join the \u003cabbr title=\"Government Communications Headquarters\"\u003eGCHQ\u003c/abbr\u003e Legal Team in Intelligence Agencies’ procurement and commercial function.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eProviding sound commercial function and sound commercial legal advice on a broad portfolio of commercial matters, including major procurements and projects, commercial policy and standard terms of conditions, major negotiations, dispute resolution and avoidance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile the role is challenging, our flexible working policy ensures a healthy work-life balance. Wherever possible, we accommodate reduced hours or job share options, balanced against business needs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Government Communications Headquarters\"\u003eGCHQ\u003c/abbr\u003e is also recruiting a \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/legal-adviser-commercial-vacancy-in-the-government-communications-headquarters-gchq\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eSenior Commercial Lawyer\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/legal-adviser-construction-and-property-vacancy-in-the-government-communications-headquarters-gchq\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eLegal Adviser - Construction and Property.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"key-responsibilities\"\u003eKey responsibilities\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBeing the day to day contact for clients, advising on a range of legal matters including:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eDrafting contracts, tender documents and advice\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eAdvising on traditional and novel approaches to contracting\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eSupporting clients on negotiations\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eAdvising on NDAs and conflicts of interest\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eAttending and contributing to project boards, contributing to board papers, business cases and legal risk papers\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eProviding training to clients and other lawyers in the team\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eLiaising with external stakeholders on legal issues\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eAdvising on dispute resolution and avoidance, assessing contractual positions and potential claims.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"apply\"\u003eApply\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor further information on the post and to apply, please visit the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://recruitmentservices.applicationtrack.com/vx/lang-en-GB/mobile-0/appcentre-3/brand-4/xf-652f2855c6e8/candidate/so/pm/1/pl/6/opp/1700\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Government Communications Headquarters\"\u003eGCHQ\u003c/abbr\u003e Careers Website\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"contact\"\u003eContact\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor application enquiries, please contact the \u003ca href=\"mailto:careers@recruitmentteam.org.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Government Communications Headquarters\"\u003eGCHQ\u003c/abbr\u003e Recruitment Team\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
